# AI tool skill-pack auto-materializations under .agents/skills/
# Per OPERATOR_DECISION_MATRIX #25 closure 2026-05-25 PM cycle 2 - Option B (platform-wide).
# Targets the specific auto-materialization pattern (duplicate dirs under .agents/skills/<skill>/),
# NOT top-level .claude/.junie/.windsurf which IS tracked substrate content (e.g., .claude/PLATFORM/).
.agents/skills/**/.claude/
.agents/skills/**/.junie/
.agents/skills/**/.windsurf/
